FROM ubuntu:xenial

COPY . /diefarbe

    curl -f -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_8.x | bash - && \
    apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y nodejs && \
    npm install && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

ENTRYPOINT ["node", "/diefarbe/dist/index.js"]
